query_text: Which warehouses are currently below their restock threshold based on stock level and capacity?
sql_query:
SELECT w."WarehouseID", w."WarehouseStreetAddress", wps."StockLevel"
FROM "robot_vacuum_depot"."Warehouse" w
JOIN "robot_vacuum_depot"."WarehouseProductStock" wps ON w."WarehouseID" = wps."WarehouseID"
WHERE wps."StockLevel" < wps."RestockThreshold"
ORDER BY wps."StockLevel" ASC
LIMIT 15

query_text: Which robot vacuum models have the highest number of delayed deliveries across all Chicago ZIP codes?
sql_query:
SELECT pr."ModelNumber", COUNT(o."OrderID") as delayed_deliveries
FROM "robot_vacuum_depot"."Order" o
JOIN "robot_vacuum_depot"."Product" pr ON o."ProductID" = pr."ProductID"
WHERE o."DeliveryStatus" = 'Delayed' AND o."DeliveryZipCode" LIKE '606%'
GROUP BY pr."ModelNumber"
ORDER BY delayed_deliveries DESC
LIMIT 15

query_text: Among all manufacturers, who has the best average review rating for their products?
sql_query:
SELECT m."ManufacturerName", AVG(r."ProductRating") as average_rating
FROM "robot_vacuum_depot"."Manufacturer" m
JOIN "robot_vacuum_depot"."Product" p ON m."ManufacturerID" = p."ManufacturerID"
JOIN "robot_vacuum_depot"."Review" r ON p."ProductID" = r."ProductID"
GROUP BY m."ManufacturerName"
ORDER BY average_rating DESC
LIMIT 15

query_text: Plot the average review rating per manufacturer to analyze product satisfaction by brand.
sql_query:
SELECT m."ManufacturerName",
       ROUND(AVG(r."ProductRating")::numeric, 2) as avg_rating
FROM "robot_vacuum_depot"."Manufacturer" m
JOIN "robot_vacuum_depot"."Product" p ON m."ManufacturerID" = p."ManufacturerID"
JOIN "robot_vacuum_depot"."Review" r ON p."ProductID" = r."ProductID"
GROUP BY m."ManufacturerName"
HAVING COUNT(r."ReviewID") >= 5
ORDER BY avg_rating DESC
LIMIT 15
